text: Lamin Charty (born 8 April 1996) is a Gambian international footballer who plays for AS Douanes, as a midfielder. ==Career== Born in Busumbala, he has played club football for Banjul Hawks and AS Douanes. He made his international debut for Gambia in 2015. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Gambian footballers Category:The Gambia international footballers Category:Banjul Hawks FC players Category:AS Douanes (Senegal) players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Gambian expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Senegal Category:Gambian expatriate sportspeople in Senegal
